  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You are surrounded by a divine aura that extends 1 Space&nbsp;in every direction from you. While creatures are within&nbsp;your aura, you can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 MP</strong> to cause 1 of the&nbsp;following effects:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Heal:</strong> You gain a pool of healing that you can use to heal any&nbsp;number of creatures within your aura, distributing the HP&nbsp;among them.</p>\n<p>Make a<strong> DC 10 Spell Check</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success:</strong> You can restore up to 3 HP.</p>\n<p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> +1 HP.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure:</strong> You only restore up to 2 HP.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Cure:&nbsp;</strong>Select a target within your aura and attempt to remove&nbsp;1 Poison or Disease affecting the target.</p>\n<p>Make a <strong>Spell Check </strong>against the <strong>DC </strong>of the Poison or Disease.</p>\n<p><strong>Success:</strong> The chosen Poison or Disease ends on the target.</p>",
